Remarks: Displays network details.

ping google.com
Description: Test connectivity by sending ICMP packets.
(sai㉿kali)-[~]
└─$ ping -c 2 google.com
PING google.com (142.250.183.46) 56(84) bytes of data.
Remarks: Confirms connection & packet loss info.

traceroute google.com
Description: Trace the route taken by packets to a host.
(sai㉿kali)-[~]
└─$ traceroute google.com
1  router.local (192.168.1.1)
2  isp.gateway (10.0.0.1)
Remarks: Shows each hop from your PC to destination.

nmap 192.168.1.1
Description: Scan open ports and services.
(sai㉿kali)-[~]
└─$ nmap 192.168.1.1
PORT   STATE SERVICE
22/tcp open  ssh
80/tcp open  http
Remarks: Useful for security auditing.

